{
  "id": "69c48df8feeb6c8776d08f17",
  "title": "日記ページの役割",
  "created": 1774489083,
  "updated": 1774512317,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c48df8feeb6c8776d08f17",
      "text": "日記ページの役割",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774489083,
      "updated": 1774489083
    },
    {
      "id": "69c48dfa00000000002af27f",
      "text": "主に[井戸端日記]の役割",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774489083,
      "updated": 1774489118
    },
    {
      "id": "69c48e2000000000002af281",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774489120,
      "updated": 1774489120
    },
    {
      "id": "69c48e2000000000002af282",
      "text": "実験、テストとしての側面",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774489121,
      "updated": 1774489145
    },
    {
      "id": "69c48e3900000000002af283",
      "text": "　Scrapbox（Cosense）で日記を書いたらどうなるか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774489146,
      "updated": 1774489192
    },
    {
      "id": "69c48e6b00000000002af284",
      "text": "　[共同日記]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774489195,
      "updated": 1774489210
    },
    {
      "id": "69c48ea800000000002af285",
      "text": "　 同じ日付に複数人が日記を書く",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774489256,
      "updated": 1774489257
    },
    {
      "id": "69c48e0700000000002af280",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774489096,
      "updated": 1774489096
    },
    {
      "id": "69c48eab00000000002af286",
      "text": "Scrapbox（Cosense）の書き込み練習としての側面",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774489259,
      "updated": 1774489302
    },
    {
      "id": "69c48eb300000000002af287",
      "text": "　タイトルを決めずに書きこめる場",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774489267,
      "updated": 1774489338
    },
    {
      "id": "69c48f0000000000002af289",
      "text": "　敷居が低い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774489345,
      "updated": 1774489352
    },
    {
      "id": "69c4902f00000000002af293",
      "text": "　[心理的安全性]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774489648,
      "updated": 1774489663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c48ef800000000002af288",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774489337,
      "updated": 1774489337
    },
    {
      "id": "69c48f1000000000002af28a",
      "text": "コミュニケーションの場としての側面",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774489360,
      "updated": 1774489408
    },
    {
      "id": "69c48fbf00000000002af291",
      "text": " [キュレーション]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774489536,
      "updated": 1774489710
    },
    {
      "id": "69c48fec00000000002af292",
      "text": " [集合知]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774489581,
      "updated": 1774489803
    },
    {
      "id": "69c492490000000000f91608",
      "text": " [動線]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774490187,
      "updated": 1774490189
    },
    {
      "id": "69c48f2b00000000002af28b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774489387,
      "updated": 1774489387
    },
    {
      "id": "69c48f5b00000000002af28c",
      "text": "個人的な記録としての側面",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774489435,
      "updated": 1774489778
    },
    {
      "id": "69c4916c00000000002af294",
      "text": " 出来事の記録",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774489965,
      "updated": 1774489966
    },
    {
      "id": "69c4916e00000000002af295",
      "text": " 行動ログ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774489967,
      "updated": 1774489992
    },
    {
      "id": "69c48f6700000000002af28e",
      "text": "　[備忘録]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774489447,
      "updated": 1774489472
    },
    {
      "id": "69c48f8100000000002af28f",
      "text": "　[内省]・[自己理解]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774489474,
      "updated": 1774489511
    },
    {
      "id": "69c48f6100000000002af28d",
      "text": "　[自己啓発]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774489441,
      "updated": 1774489531
    },
    {
      "id": "69c49e4300000000003e62b9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774493251,
      "updated": 1774493251
    },
    {
      "id": "69c49e4300000000003e62ba",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774493251,
      "updated": 1774493251
    },
    {
      "id": "69c49e4300000000003e62bb",
      "text": "---",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774493251,
      "updated": 1774493281
    },
    {
      "id": "69c49e6100000000003e62bc",
      "text": "個人のプロジェクトの日付タイトルのページの役割",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774493281,
      "updated": 1774493311
    },
    {
      "id": "69c49e7e00000000003e62c0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774493311,
      "updated": 1774493311
    },
    {
      "id": "69c49e7800000000003e62be",
      "text": "[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774493304,
      "updated": 1774493306
    },
    {
      "id": "69c4b0ab000000000055c5c2",
      "text": " [ライフログ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774497963,
      "updated": 1774512317
    },
    {
      "id": "69c4b0b4000000000055c5c3",
      "text": " まとめ的な事もしたい",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774497972,
      "updated": 1774497979
    },
    {
      "id": "69c4b0c3000000000055c5c4",
      "text": " 雑なメモの場所にするか？",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774497988,
      "updated": 1774498005
    },
    {
      "id": "69c4b0cc000000000055c5c5",
      "text": "  logseqならするかも",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774497996,
      "updated": 1774498001
    },
    {
      "id": "69c4b0dd000000000055c5c6",
      "text": "  日記的ではないことはたいていinboxのタグを行につけておいて、日の終わりに転機、消される。",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774498013,
      "updated": 1774498051
    },
    {
